main event: A round white object with a hazy brown color was seen in motion with no sound in Challenge, California on July 12, 1956.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 60 seconds., The object was observed visually from the ground., The object traveled in a straight course., It is suggested that the object may have been a balloon, aircraft, or space body., The report was part of the Project Blue Book UFO investigation program.
witness description: Ground visual observation by an unmentioned individual.
